msgstr "Your request has been forwarded to a technician."

msgid ""
"Voulez-vous être pris en charge directement par un technicien humain, sans "
"passer par l'assistant IA ?"
msgstr ""
"Do you want to be taken in charge directly by a human technician, without "
"going through the AI assistant?"

msgid ""
"À la création d'un ticket, ce module tente de proposer une solution de "
"niveau 1 (sans droits administrateur ni compétence technique) directement "
"dans le ticket. S'il n'a pas assez d'éléments, il pose des questions de "
"clarification puis réattribue le ticket au groupe défini ci-dessous."
msgstr ""
"When a ticket is created, this module tries to suggest a level-1 solution "
"(no admin rights or technical skill required) directly in the ticket. If it "
"doesn't have enough information, it asks clarifying questions then reassigns"
" the ticket to the group defined below."

msgid ""
"🙋 L'utilisateur a demandé à être pris en charge directement par un "
"technicien."
msgstr ""
"🙋 The user has requested to be taken in charge directly by a technician."

msgid "🤖 Assistant IA — Suggestion de résolution :"
msgstr "🤖 AI Assistant — Suggested solution:"

msgid "Level 1 Assistant - Ticket #%d Analysis (round %d)."
msgstr "Level 1 Assistant - Ticket #%d Analysis (round %d)."

msgid ""
"🤖 Assistant IA : merci pour ces précisions. J'ai encore besoin de quelques "
"éléments :"
msgstr ""
"🤖 AI Assistant: thank you for these details. I still need a few more things:"

msgid ""
"🤖 Assistant IA : merci pour ces précisions. Je ne suis malheureusement pas "
"en mesure de résoudre ce ticket seul, un technicien va prendre le relais."
msgstr ""
"🤖 AI Assistant: thank you for these details. Unfortunately I'm not able to "
"resolve this ticket on my own, a technician will take over."

msgid ""
"🤖 Assistant IA : pourriez-vous préciser quelques points pour m'aider à vous "
"proposer une solution ?"
msgstr ""
"🤖 AI Assistant: could you clarify a few points to help me suggest a "
"solution?"

msgid ""
"AI Level 1 Assistant: processes queued ticket analyses and follow-up replies"
" in the background."
msgstr ""
"AI Level 1 Assistant: processes queued ticket analyses and follow-up replies"
" in the background."

msgid ""
"Processes AI Level 1 Assistant ticket analyses and follow-up replies in the "
"background."
msgstr ""
"Processes AI Level 1 Assistant ticket analyses and follow-up replies in the "
"background."

msgid "Désactiver l'IA"
msgstr "Disable AI"

msgid "Assistant IA"
msgstr "AI Assistant"

msgid ""
"Ce groupe sera créé automatiquement à la prochaine installation/mise à jour "
"du plugin."
msgstr ""
"This group will be created automatically at the next plugin install/upgrade."

msgid ""
"Créé et géré automatiquement par le plugin : chaque ticket pris en charge "
"par l'IA y est assigné le temps qu'elle s'en occupe, et il en est retiré dès"
" que l'utilisateur désactive l'IA, qu'un technicien répond directement, ou "
"que le ticket est réattribué au groupe d'escalade ci-dessous."
msgstr ""
"Created and managed automatically by the plugin: every ticket the AI is "
"handling is assigned to it for as long as it works on it, and removed as "
"soon as the user disables the AI, a technician replies directly, or the "
"ticket is reassigned to the escalation group below."

msgid "Groupe \"Assistant IA\""
msgstr "\"AI Assistant\" group"

msgid ""
"Groupe auquel le ticket est réattribué uniquement lorsque l'IA ne peut plus "
"l'aider elle-même (nombre de tours de questions atteint) et qu'elle n'a pas "
"été désactivée manuellement. En cas de désactivation manuelle ou de prise en"
" charge par un technicien, le ticket est simplement désassigné (Tickets "
"entrants)."
msgstr ""
"Group to which the ticket is reassigned only when the AI can no longer help "
"on its own (question round limit reached) and it hasn't been manually "
"disabled. On manual opt-out or technician takeover, the ticket is simply "
"unassigned (Incoming tickets)."

msgid ""
"Groupe créé automatiquement par le plugin AI Suite : les tickets pris en "
"charge par l'Assistant IA Niveau 1 y sont assignés temporairement."
msgstr ""
"Group created automatically by the AI Suite plugin: tickets handled by the "
"Level 1 AI Assistant are temporarily assigned to it."

